PhotoCradle is an elegant javascript widget wrapping your photo collection.

Demo page: http://ytiurin.github.io/jsphotocradle/

What is so special about PhotoCradle:
- Original "infinite" thumbnails bar
- On-demand image loading
- Fast and adaptive fullpage browsing mode
- Multiple cradles per page
- Integration with popular services (flickr, picasa)
- Skins based on CSS theming
